strings: <voice_0x01000FE8><se_def>*: So you managed to get the royal Argonian mirror!

<voice_0x01000FE9><se_def>*: I don't know how you got hold of it,
but now we can finally get inside and fight Dhoulmagus! Well done!

<voice_0x01000FEA><se_def>*: Right!
Er...well then, I'll just go and fetch my men!
<voice_0x01000FEB><se_def>*: That won't do any good. Even if it's the same size, without any magic power, the mirror can't break through the dark aura.
